title: Grimm Fairy Tales - Different Seasons TPB (v01 + v02) (2011 + 20
description:
Grimm Fairy Tales - Different Seasons TPB (v01 + v02) (2011 + 2012) (Digital) 
(K6-Empire) 


The first two out of four Trade Paperbacks collecting some of Zenescope's most popular One-Shots and Holiday Specials from the Grimm Fairy Tales universe.

Volume #1

Contains the Las Vegas Annual (2009), Halloween Special #1 (2009), Holiday Edition #1 (2009), and Giant-Size #1 (2008).

Volume #2

Includes Grimm Fairy Tales Holiday Edition #3 (2011), Halloween Special #3 (2011), and Grimm Fairy Tales Annual #1 (2007) and Titanic Annual #2 (2008).
